Package: transcriptomicsPipeline
Type: Package
Title: Xenopus Transcriptomics Analysis Pipeline
Version: 1.0.0
Authors@R: c(person("Allison Grossberg", email = "allison.grossberg@wyss.harvard.edu", role = c("aut", "cre")))
Description: A comprehensive R package for transcriptomics data analysis including data import, cleaning, differential expression analysis, gene mapping, PCA, and gene set enrichment analysis. Supports both Pluto API and local data sources.
